Who we are
We are IMG, which includes IMG Worldwide, LLC and affiliated entities. We are also part of Endeavor and may share data with its affiliated entities (“Endeavor”).
IMG is a global leader in sports, fashion, events and media. We manage some of the world’s greatest athletes and fashion icons; own and operate hundreds of live events annually; and are a leading independent producer and distributor of sports and entertainment media. We also specialize in licensing, sports training, and league development.
Like any company, we use a variety of third party businesses and partners to market and provide our Services to you. Some of those companies are part of Endeavor and some are third parties that we partner with or support our operations so we can provide the best experience to you.
